                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_2292">جوامع الحكايات ولوامع الروايات</title>
                     <note>Only part of the work. F1a: a) Signature: ... ham 18th August 1811 b) Stamp, the name and date in ink: Presented to the ROYAL ASIATIC SOCIETY by Lieut Colonel C.J. Doyle 15th of March 1834. F1b: Ex libris C.J. Doyle A.D. 1820. Contains parts of the first and second Qisms of the work. In the manuscript the title is given as Jami' al-Hikayat. Headings and punctuation in red. On blue paper.</note>
